---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Roll up disk consumption by sender, mimetype, or label

Usage: mxr storage [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --by <BY>            Group by which dimension. One of: sender, mimetype, label [default: sender] [possible values: sender, mimetype, label]
      --limit <LIMIT>      Maximum buckets to return [default: 50]
      --account <ACCOUNT>  Restrict to a single account by id
      --format <FORMAT>    [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help               Print help
